    </Annotation>
    <Annotation>
        <AnnotationProperty IRI="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/description"/>
        <Literal>This vocabulary provides a formal semantic representation of the modelling centres contributing to the CORDEX–CMIP5 ensemble and used in the Copernicus C3S Interactive Atlas. Each institution is described as an individual of the datasource:ModellingCenter class from the METACLIP ‘datasource’ ontology, enabling consistent institutional identification, cross‑ontology interoperability, and machine‑readable integration with C3S provenance and climate‑data records</Literal>
    </Annotation>
    <Annotation>
        <AnnotationProperty IRI="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/title"/>
        <Literal>C3S-CORDEX-CMIP5 Institution Vocabulary</Literal>
    </Annotation>
